## Summary
This documentation page explains how to install and configure the Amplitude Guides and Surveys SDK for websites and applications, covering integration methods with Amplitude Browser SDK, third-party analytics providers, and Google Tag Manager, along with API methods for theme management, callbacks, routing, localization, and guide/survey control.

